  "text": "For secondary transplantation, 3 Â 10 6 total BM cells from primary recipients were mixed with 300 000 BtkÀ/À spleen cells and were transplanted into lethally irradiated BtkÀ/À secondary recipients. Reconstitution in peripheral blood was monitored every 4 weeks after transplantation. At 20 weeks after transplantation, mice were killed and analyzed for reconstitution in tissues as described previously. [CITATION_1] ",
